&lt;th&gt;Starting Price&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Zapier&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Integrating apps&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Workflow automation, multi-step Zaps&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Free, paid plans from $19.99/month&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;UiPath&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Robotic process automation&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Advanced RPA capabilities, AI integration&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Contact for pricing&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;HubSpot&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;CRM and marketing automation&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Email marketing, lead management&lt;/td&gt;
